## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **One Health paradigm 의의** — animal+human+ecosystem 통합 framework (WHO/FAO/WOAH 2008 tripartite + 2022 quadripartite UNEP 추가). drug discovery 측면에서 zoonotic spillover + cross-species + xenotransplant 가 actionable subset.
2. **Lyme VLA15 2026 first FDA Lyme vaccine 50+ years 만** — LYMErix 2002 withdraw 후 처음. quantum-VQE 의 OspA epitope optimization 가능.
3. **Qdenga 2024 dengue paradigm** — Dengvaxia 2019 의 seropositive-only 한계 극복, broader serotype coverage. quantum-VQE 의 NS5 RdRp / E protein 측면 candidate.
4. **xenotransplant 2022 첫 pig kidney transplant** — eGenesis / Revivicor 10-gene pig (GGTA1/CMAH/B4GalNT2 KO + hCD46/hCD55/hTBM/hHO1/hCD47/hEPCR KI). 2022 Bennett pig heart, 2024 NYU pig kidney case. AAV / VIROCAPSID axis 의 자연 cross-link.
5. **COVID-19 origin 논쟁** — bat coronavirus spillover + intermediate host (pangolin / raccoon dog 등) 미해결. zoonotic surveillance 의 lesson.
6. **Nipah Disease X status** — WHO R&D Blueprint priority pathogen, mortality 40-75%, no FDA. mRNA universal Henipavirus 가 가장 promising path.
7. **한국 cross-link** — 농림축산검역본부 (APQA) + 식약처 (MFDS) cross-jurisdiction. drug discovery 측면 한정으로 본 entry 는 식약처 zoonotic vaccine FDA equivalent path 만 cover, surveillance / policy 는 scope 외.
8. **scope discipline 명시** — AMR (antimicrobial resistance) policy / animal antibiotic stewardship 명시 제외 (`.roadmap.disease_infectious` cross-link). surveillance / climate change / ecosystem 명시 제외. drug discovery 만 cover.
9. **animal-derived therapeutic 의 historical paradigm** — captopril (1981, pit viper bradykinin → ACE inhibitor) 가 대표 historical. bee venom melittin / snake venom / cone snail conotoxin 등 research 진행 중. quantum-VQE 의 peptide pocket 측면 cover.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, One Health 임상 의미 한정. PLANETARY-HEALTH axis REJECT 의 정당성 (drug discovery 외부 surveillance / policy / ecosystem 가 5-axis 와 orthogonal 아닌 disjoint 임을 confirm).

